fields.news_heading: Career Path was the first seminar under #digitalkondotty
fields.news_content: Career Path was the first seminar under #digitalkondotty to spread awareness about the world of technology on 30th June 2022 at GT Hall. The seminars were conducted on three topics, Tech Training - by K C Musthafa (Founder & CEO of Gedexo Technologies), Student Mentoring Program -by Aswathi Ramachandran (Consultant & Psychologist) and Career Hacking Program - by Ajmal T P (Founding Chief Brand Buji). The program was mainly focusing on delivering guidance to the students for boosting their careers.

The uprising evolution of technology has both adverse and beneficial impacts on the public. Cyber Security was yet another event conducted by #digitalkondotty on 03-Sep-2022. The program successfully delivered positive impacts on the audiences about the adversities and benefits of technologies. The weak points and attacks through the internet are well explained to the public along with the solutions to these cyber threats. In this fast-growing technical world, cyber security is a must to protect ourselves from threats around the globe.
